{"tid":775241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又嚟水舞間  東鐵太和站月台漏水　","createTime":"2018-08-11T04:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T06:43:22.000Z","uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"696b866509ce7def4c82a205914c408def63de1b","tid":775241,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180811/s00001/83884948e8646d57f9721f399837bed4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180811%2Fs00001%2F83884948e8646d57f9721f399837bed4.jpg&h=672017b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天文台在今早7時15分發出黃色暴雨警告信號，有網民8時半左右在社交網站上載一段東鐵太和站月台懷疑漏水情況的影片，抱怨「出面入面都落大雨」，千幾億拎咗去挖窿，年年加車費，幾時肯畀錢改善月台」，「覺得真係咬佢食呀」。<br />\n<br />\n據網民Siu Yuen在facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」上載的太和站月台懷疑漏水影片，月台近窗邊的位置漏水，順着牆身流到地面，地面亦有有大攤水漬。Siu Yuen回應《明報》查詢時表示，不知道漏水是否由天花開始滲入，但當時情況猶如瀑布，認為很危險，所以他也不敢走太近，恐怕會漏電。<br />\n<br />\nSiu Yuen稱，本身住在大埔，指太和站内不時會有這種情況，不是近期才發生，而且不一定要大雨到黃雨程度才會漏水，只要下大雨就有漏水可能，更形容「出面大雨，入面（月台）細雨」。<br />\n<br />\n影片上載短短一小時，已經有近200人以「心情」回應，當中近55人表示「嘩」，52人表示「嬲嬲」。亦有網民留言稱情況已持續很久，「九廣鐵路時期已經係咁，吞併咗之後只係識搞靚個月台，分返開算啦，世界級鐵路喎」；「其他唔知，但上水、太和九龍塘都係咁架啦」；又有網民幽默留言稱，「入面幾大雨」，「又嚟香港水舞間！」，「室內瀑布，好貴㗎」；更有網民挖苦港鐵說，「計我話，MTR專心做地產，火車生意交畀孟加拉國鐵路局做」。<br />\n<br />\n明報記者已就有關情況聯絡港鐵，現正等候回覆。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mingpaoinews/videos/1925856267474499/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmingpaoinews%2Fvideos%2F1925856267474499%2F&d=Oduy08sX6Lr3Yv6xxZYNff9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=98bad92e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mingpaoinews/videos/1925856267474499/</a>"},{"pid":"01b2ca299e2d170ec932065c8ac75823997cad89","tid":775241,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"馬時亨：全世界都讚緊我哋，係香港人鬧我地"},{"pid":"0b663a704b4b672e040065d4355c09cea74b2070","tid":775241,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:40:23.000Z","msg":"太和果d 支柱係不銹鋼起<br />\n唔係石屎<br />\n<br />\n天花只係用隔音屏加建<br />\n唔係原本建築<br />\n<br />\n原來都係露天設計"},{"pid":"9ac8f6fa9abaef690ee188144c15f3a50adb3d7c","tid":775241,"uid":28583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b2ca299e2d170ec932065c8ac75823997cad89","tid":775241,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"馬時亨：全世界都讚緊我哋，係香港人鬧我地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fe60c50fafb6cfe5eb063281a2ce3ce28e6fe8","tid":775241,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/144301_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F144301_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ee1bb9b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cdd185c71fad89582621c69253594a8c876714e","tid":775241,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/26144643/image1527317171380.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F26144643%2Fimage1527317171380.png&h=340db408&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}